{"word":"G1606 - ἐκπνέω - ekpnéō - ek-pneh'-o - Give up the ghost","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκπνέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ekpnéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-pneh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Give up the ghost</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஜீவனை விடு"},{"paragraph":"to breathe out, breathe out one's life, breathe one's last, expire"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G4154 - πνέω - pnéō - pneh'-o/4154\">G4154</a>; to <i>expire:</i> - give up the ghost.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1606/1606\">G1606</a>, <a href=\"#/G2315/2315\">G2315</a>, <a href=\"#/G4151/4151\">G4151</a>, <a href=\"#/G4152/4152\">G4152</a>, <a href=\"#/G4153/4153\">G4153</a>, <a href=\"#/G4154/4154\">G4154</a>"}]}